{"word":"στοιχέω","slug":"στοιχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στοιχέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στοῖχος'><el>στοῖχος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to go in a line</i> or <i>row: to go in battle-order</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <i>to be in line with, walk by</i> rule or principle, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}